item.title: Latest Releases of Eclipse Temurin - The Open Source Java SE Build
item.description: The Adoptium website provides access to the latest releases of Eclipse Temurin, an open source Java SE build based on OpenJDK. Temurin is available for a wide range of platforms and Java SE versions, and the latest releases recommended for production use are listed on this page. Some key details about the Temurin releases: Latest Recommended Releases The page displays the current recommended Temurin releases for production use, which include versions 22, 21, 19, 18, 16, and 8 (LTS).
